<div class='commit-subject'>xkb: Handle xkb formated string output safely (CVE-2017-13723)</div><div class='commit-msg'>Generating strings for XKB data used a single shared static buffer,
which offered several opportunities for errors. Use a ring of
resizable buffers instead, to avoid problems when strings end up
longer than anticipated.

